<!DOCTYPE html>
<html data-ng-app="spaceFrontierApp">
<% include header %>


<body class="container" data-ng-controller="dataController">
    <% include navbar %>
    <h1>Data Selection</h1>
    <p>Bacon ipsum dolor amet pariatur esse in, strip steak pork pastrami proident culpa in cillum fugiat ut turkey. Cow pork loin minim duis, labore ball tip ipsum swine in eiusmod dolore kevin ad. Pariatur filet mignon ham hock, sed eiusmod in pork chop fatback chuck. Tail ut cillum shank laboris meatball. Tenderloin enim ground round chuck incididunt officia. Ipsum tempor turkey andouille.</p>
    <hr>
    <h3>User Input</h3>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div>
                <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
                    <li class="active"><a href="#tab1">Channels</a></li>
                    <li>               <a href="#tab2">Arrays</a></li>
                    <li>               <a href="#tab3">Bits/Second</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section id="tab1" class="tab-content active">
        <div class="dividersmall"></div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                Channels 
               
                <div class="input-group">
                     <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="channel" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="Channels">Channels</span>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>
                Bits/Channel: 

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="bitschannel" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="Bits/Channel">Bits/Channel</span>
                </div>


                <div class="divider"></div>
                Integrations/Second:
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="integrations1" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="Integrations/Second">Integrations/Second</span>
                </div>
                <div class="divider"></div>
                Percent of Time Generating Data:
                <div class="input-group">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input class="form-control" placeholder="10" data-ng-model="resolution1" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="percent">% of time</span>
                </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class = "dividerlarge"></div>
                    <div id="button">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" id="round" ng-click="tabCHANNELS()" ng-disabled="channel==null||bitschannel==null||integrations1==null ||resolution1==null||channel.length==0||bitschannel==0||resolution1==0||integrations1.length==0">
                            Calculate
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
    </section>


    <section id="tab2" class="tab-content hide">
        <div class="dividersmall"></div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                Array Size - x: 

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="sizex" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="pixelsX"> pixels</span>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>
                Array Size - y: 


                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text"class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="sizey" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="pixelsY"> pixels</span>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>
                Integrations/Second:

                <div class="input-group">
                     <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="integrations2" valid-number/>
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="pixelsY"> Integrations/Second</span>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>                 
                Percent of Time Generating Data:
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" valid-number class="form-control" placeholder="10" data-ng-model="resolution2"/>
                    <div class="input-group-addon">% of time</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class = "dividerlarge"></div>
                    <div id="button">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" id="round" ng-click="tabARRAY()" ng-disabled="sizex==null||sizey==null||integrations2==null||resolution2==null||sizex.length==0||sizey.length==0||integrations2.length==0||resolution2.length==0">
                            Calculate
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
    </section>

    <section id="tab3" class="tab-content hide">
        <div class="dividersmall"></div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                Bits/Second 

                <div class="input-group">
                     <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="100" data-ng-model="bitssecond" valid-number/>
                    <div class="input-group-addon">Bits/Second</div>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>
                Percent of Time Generating Data:
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="10" data-ng-model="resolution3" valid-number/>
                    <div class="input-group-addon">% of time</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class = "dividerlarge"></div>
                    <div id="button">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" id="round" ng-click="tabBPS()" ng-disabled="bitssecond==null||resolution3==null||bitssecond.length==0||resolution3.length==0">
                            Calculate
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
    </section>

    <div ng-show="showCalculate">
        <h3>Calculation Results</h3>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class = "divider"></div>
                Bits/Second:

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" data-ng-model="totalbits" readonly="readonly" valid-number/>
                    <div class="input-group-addon">Bits/Second</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class = "divider"></div>
                Required Downlink:

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" data-ng-model="totaldownlink" readonly="readonly"/>
                    <div class="input-group-addon">MIPS</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class = "dividerlarge"></div>
                    <div id="button">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" id="round" ng-click="nextCDH()">
                            Select CDH
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div ng-show="showDatabase">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Available CDH 
                    <div class="btn-group">
                        <button class="btn btn-default btn-xs dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                        Show:
                        <span class="caret"></span>
                        </button>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <div class="checkbox">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios1" value="option1" data-ng-model="OBC">
                                        Onboard Comp.
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="checkbox">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios1" value="option1" data-ng-model="bus">
                                        Bus
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="checkbox">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios1" value="option1" data-ng-model="imageprocessor">
                                        Image Processor
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="btn-group">
                        <button class="btn btn-default btn-xs dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                        Sort By: 
                        <span class="caret"></span>
                        </button>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <div class="radio">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" ng-model= "sort" value="Mass">
                                        Mass
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="radio">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" ng-model= "sort" value="Power">
                                        Power
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="radio">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" ng-model= "sort" value="Volume">
                                        Volume
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </h3>
                <h6>Double click on the info button to learn more about a part, or on the right arrow to add it to the existing CubeSat.</h6>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-11">
                        <div class = "dividersmall"></div>
                        <select multiple class="form-control" size="14">
                            <option ng-click="savePart(part)" ng-repeat="part in cdhparts|filter:okType|filter:okData|orderBy:order">
                                {{part.Name}}
                            </option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-1">
                        <a type="button" ng-click="showInfo()" id="pushdown1" class="btn btn-sm btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span></a>
                        <a type="button" ng-click="addPart()" id="pushdown2" class="btn btn-sm btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Current Design</h3>
                <h6>Command & Data Handling Selection<br>Page 5/7</h6>
                <div class = "dividersmall"></div>
                <select multiple class="form-control" size="14">
                    <option>Target: {{target}}</option>
                    <option>Instrumentation:{{instrumentPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Attitude: {{attitudePart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Propulsion: {{propulsionPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Ground Station: {{stationPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Antenna: {{antennaPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Receiver: {{receiverPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>CDH: {{cdhPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Solar Panels: {{panelsPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Batteries: {{batteriesPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>EPS: {{epsPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Bus: {{busPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Deployer: {{deployerPart.Name}}</option>
                    <option>Thermal: {{thermalPart.Name}}</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class = "divider"></div>
                <nav>
                <ul class="pager">
                    <button type="button" class='btn btn-default' id="round" ng-click="prevPage()" style="float: left; color:#0099CC; border: false">Previous Page <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></button>

                    <button type="button" class='btn btn-default' id="round" ng-click="nextPage()" style="float: right; color:#0099CC; border: false" ng-disabled="cdhPart==null">Next Page <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></button>
                </ul>
                </nav>  
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
    </div>
    <% include footer %>
    <div class = "divider"></div>
</body>

</html>